78th Street, west side, just south of Thirty-second Avenue, 78th Street is to the right of Trains Meadow Road (now 1935 non-existent) showing in a set of 4 views the Wright farmhouse. Views 2, 3 and 4, show a closer view of the house.

March 1923
View 2: Oct. 1, 1925
View 3: May 1927
View 4: April 1923

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection

The house is also known as the "Black Watch Headquarters."
